    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. It has been meticulously maintained with a full service history, ensuring that it drives as perfectly as it looks. Every feature and electronic component functions exactly as intended, making this an ideal choice for a discerning buyer who demands the very best.",
