    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation at a lower price point. While the car starts and drives, it shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dents on the body, and significant wear on the interior upholstery. Mechanically, it is operational, but it will likely require some preventative maintenance soon, such as new tires and a brake service. All major systems like the AC and radio work, though the engine has a minor oil leak that should be monitored. It is a reliable daily driver for those who don't mind a bit of character and some upcoming DIY projects.",
